note right of BaseScraper
**Improvements:**
- Clear separation of concerns
- Dependency injection for all dependencies
- Pipeline pattern for processing stages
- Strategy pattern for parsing & validation
end note

note right of ProcessingPipeline
**Pipeline Pattern:**
- Flexible stage composition
- Easy to add/remove stages
- Each stage is independent
- Clear data flow
end note

note right of BaseParser
**Strategy Pattern:**
- Interchangeable parsing strategies
- Easy to extend with new parsers
- Separation of extraction & parsing
end note

note right of FieldNormalizer
**Strategy Pattern:**
- Type-specific normalization
- Extensible for new types
- Reusable across factories
end note

note right of BaseValidator
**Composite Pattern:**
- Composed of validation rules
- Easy to add/remove rules
- Stats collection separated
end note

@enduml
